            <div class="title">
                Education Bill (Government Defeat)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1944-03-29/debates/9bd3630d-376c-45ba-ac66-25908bd79488/RoyalAssent" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
